<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 14:17:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比特币自 FTX 崩盘以来最糟糕的一周可能预示着未来还会有更多痛苦</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-09/bitcoin-s-worst-week-since-ftx-crash-may-signal-more-pain-ahead</link><description>上周五，比特币跌破 60,000 美元，结束了自 2022 年 Sam Bankman-Fried 的 FTX 交易所倒闭以来最糟糕的一周。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iF.swEnhGzwg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 10:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-09/bitcoin-s-worst-week-since-ftx-crash-may-signal-more-pain-ahead</guid></item><item><title>比特币 2350 亿美元的暴跌掩盖了加密货币领域的更大转变</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/bitcoin-s-235-billion-crash-masks-a-bigger-shift-across-crypto</link><description>过去，理解加密货币最简单的方法就是研究比特币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1vQXSA8jnFI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 15:56:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/bitcoin-s-235-billion-crash-masks-a-bigger-shift-across-crypto</guid></item><item><title>FTX 联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 申请特朗普赦免</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/ftx-co-founder-bankman-fried-formally-applies-for-trump-pardon</link><description>FTX 联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 正式申请总统赦免，两年多前，他因其曾经繁荣的加密货币帝国数十亿美元的崩溃而被定罪。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igLrG_nQWWMY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 14:09:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/ftx-co-founder-bankman-fried-formally-applies-for-trump-pardon</guid></item><item><title>在稀有销售扰乱加密货币后策略恢复购买比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/strategy-resumes-buying-bitcoin-after-rare-sale-roils-crypto</link><description>在数字资产财务公司罕见的代币销售扰乱加密货币市场一周后，Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc. 恢复购买比特币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i6r8rH1LbSE0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 12:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-08/strategy-resumes-buying-bitcoin-after-rare-sale-roils-crypto</guid></item></channel></rss>